# local-cache/ holds multi-GB model assets shared across all run modes:
# docker, native dev, and the packaged Remnant.exe. Includes HuggingFace
# model weights, nginx upstream proxy cache, and the ollama model store.
#
# Nothing in here should ever reach git. Rule: ignore everything
# except this file and the .gitkeep placeholders that let subdirs
# exist before first download.

*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!hf-cache/
!nginx-cache/
!ollama-data/
!chroma-db/
hf-cache/*
nginx-cache/*
ollama-data/*
chroma-db/*
!hf-cache/.gitkeep
!nginx-cache/.gitkeep
!ollama-data/.gitkeep
!chroma-db/.gitkeep
